  • public final class CampaignLabelDelegate
extends AbstractGetMutateDelegate<com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.v201409.cm.CampaignLabel,com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.v201409.cm.CampaignLabelOperation,com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.v201409.cm.CampaignServiceInterface>
    Specific AbstractGetMutateDelegate for CampaignLabel.

    Labels are linked (ADD and REMOVE) to Campaigns using the CampaignServiceInterface, GETs in the other hand are in the LabelService.

    Implementation is not thread-safe, because AdWordsSession and Apache Axis service objects are not thread-safe.

    Author:
    Julian Toledo
